    <h1>Pipeline</h1>
    <p class="description">A visual representation of where every active prospect sits in your sales process — from first contact to closed deal — organized by stage and <strong>tracked by monetary value</strong> to enable revenue forecasting.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
